results.name: Nike Dunk Low Georgetown (PS)
results.story: The Nike Dunk Low TD ‘Georgetown’ showcases a two-tone palette inspired by the Hoyas. The leather upper is rendered in a light grey base with contrasting overlays in Dark Obsidian. No-tie elastic laces allow little feet to easily slip in and out of the shoe, while perforated detailing at the toe box yields enhanced breathability. Standard Nike branding on the heel tab and woven tongue tag project an OG aesthetic. The low-top is anchored by a rubber cupsole that pairs white sidewalls with a dark navy outsole.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Sail Multi-Camo (PS)
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Dunk Low SE PS ‘Sail Multi-Camo’ makes use of an off-white textile upper with mismatched leather overlays in clashing military-inspired prints. On the left shoe, the forefoot and heel overlays are rendered in snow and desert camo, while the right shoe features autumn and woodland camo designs in the same areas. Dark green accents land on the woven tongue tag, leather Swoosh, textile-lined interior and rubber outsole. Mismatched heel tabs are embroidered with a standard Nike wordmark on the left shoe and a basketball graphic on the right.

results.name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Hare Space Jam (PS)
results.story: Offered in little kid sizing, the Nike Air Force 1 ‘06 PS ‘Hare’ is drawn from an expansive collection celebrating the release of ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy.’ The vintage hoops shoe features a white leather upper with contrasting accents in Light Blue Fury. On the right shoe, Bugs Bunny appears on the woven tongue tag and a prominent lateral-side patch, while the left shoe features Lola Bunny’s likeness in the same spots. Underfoot, the AF1’s signature pivot-point rubber outsole delivers time-tested traction.

results.name: Nike Lebron 18 Low Summit White Space Jam (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the LeBron 18 Low PS ‘Lola Bunny’ is taken from a capsule collection celebrating LeBron James’ 2021 film, ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy.’ The color-blocked textile upper features a white base, black Swoosh and coral accents on the lateral side, and a black toe box, teal quarter panel, black Swoosh and red and blue no-sew overlays on the medial side. A Tune Squad logo lands on the adjustable strap, while mismatched insoles reveal the cartoon likenesses of LeBron James and Lola Bunny. The sneaker’s tooling comprises a two-tone foam midsole and a translucent rubber outsole in Dynamic Turquoise.

results.name: Nike Lebron 18 Low Wile E. vs Roadrunner Space Jam (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the Nike LeBron 18 Low PS ‘Wile E. x Roadrunner’ pays homage to a perpetually warring duo from ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy.’ The left shoe gives the nod to Wile E. Coyote, featuring a beige textile upper and a sockliner graphic depicting the character himself. The left shoe’s blue textile construction represents Roadrunner, whose likeness similarly graces the sockliner. Both shoes are secured with no-tie elastic laces and an adjustable ankle strap accented with a Tune Squad badge. Underfoot, a gum rubber outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Computer Chip Space Jam (PS)
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Force 1 PS ‘Computer Chip’ is taken from a comprehensive collection inspired by ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy.’ The low-top makes use of a black leather upper covered in circuit board graphics that give the nod to the film’s villainous AI. Atop the tongue, a bright blue woven Nike tag provides a vibrant pop of color. The sneaker is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole with glossy black sidewalls and a glow-in-the-dark outsole.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low UNC (2021) (PS)
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘University Blue’ showcases a simple two-tone palette that recalls the silhouette’s 1985 debut as a college team shoe. The leather upper is rendered in a stark white finish with contrasting powder blue overlays. Nike branding lands on the heel tab, woven tongue tag and foam sockliner, which combines with a padded low-cut collar to deliver a comfortable fit. The low-top is underpinned by a durable rubber outsole originally designed to grip the hardwood.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low UNDEFEATED Canteen Dunk vs. AF1 Pack (PS)
results.story: Offered in little kid sizing, the Undefeated x Nike Dunk Low SP PS ‘Canteen’ is taken from the crossover ‘Dunk vs. AF-1’ pack. The sneaker takes its cues from Undefeated’s ‘Inside Out Priority’ Air Force 1 collaboration from 2006, featuring a leather upper finished in varying shades of brown. The understated palette is enlivened by tonal prints and a contrasting hit of Lemon Frost on the leather Swoosh. Undefeated’s Five Strikes logo adorns the woven tongue tag and lateral heel.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Light Bone Tropical Twist (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘Tiffany’ adds fresh pops of color to an otherwise neutral colorway. A subtle shade of Light Bone is applied to the leather upper, contrasted by black leather overlays and a signature Swoosh in Tropical Twist — a turquoise finish that calls to mind the ‘Tiffany’ Dunk SB from 2005. The delicate hue is repeated via Nike branding on the heel tab and woven tongue tag. The sneaker rides on a full-stitch, low-profile rubber cupsole.

results.name: LeBron 18 LeBron James Family Foundation We Are Family (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the LeBron James Family Foundation x Nike LeBron 18 PS ‘We Are Family’ celebrates LeBron James’ Akron-based nonprofit organization. Varying teal hues are executed on the upper, featuring a breathable knit base with a padded mesh collar and molded TPU heel counter. LeBron’s foundation logo adorns the sockliner, while ‘We Are Family’ is inscribed on a decorative air bag affixed to the tongue. Hyper Crimson accents deliver vibrant pops of color on the sneaker’s midsole and rubber outsole.

results.name: Nike Dunk High Panda PS (2021)
Nike Air Griffey Max 1 Varsity Royal (PS) (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Griffey Max 1 PS ‘Varsity Royal’ revives Ken Griffey Jr.’s debut signature shoe in little kids sizing. Originally released in 1996, the retro trainer features a bright blue nubuck upper with contrasting white leather paneling. Volt-colored Swooshes adorn the heel and adjustable ankle strap, the latter also featuring Junior’s jersey number with the Seattle Mariners. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a foam midsole fitted with a visible Max Air unit under the heel.

results.name: Nike Air More Uptempo Bulls Hoops Pack (PS)
Nike Dunk Low Michigan (2021) (PS)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘Michigan’ brings back an OG colorway in little kids sizing. Rendered in low-top form, the retro hoops shoe features a simple two-tone design that pays homage to the Michigan Wolverines — one of the universities included in 1985’s classic ‘Be True to Your School’ pack. An all-leather upper in Varsity Maize and Midnight Navy sits atop a contrasting white midsole. Standard Nike branding decorates the woven tongue tag and heel tab.

results.name: Nike Air Max 1 CLOT Kiss of Death (2021 )(PS)
results.story: Built for little kids, the 2021 reissue of the CLOT x Nike Air Max 1 PS ‘Kiss of Death’ brings back a coveted collaboration from 2006 — the first ever joint effort between the Swoosh and Edison Chen’s streetwear brand. Updated with refreshed details, the sneaker’s standout features remain intact, including a transparent toe box, scaly red leather Swoosh and deconstructed ostrich-skin collar. They’re joined by a reflective heel overlay in red leather, along with upgraded reflexology-inspired graphics on the custom sockliner and translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low SP Orange Pearl (PS)
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘Orange Pearl’ exhibits classic color blocking that speaks to the shoe’s college basketball roots. The pastel palette on the leather upper combines an off-white base with contrasting overlays in a delicate pink hue. Nike branding lands on the heel tab, sockliner and a woven tag atop the lightly padded nylon tongue. The low-top is mounted on a standard rubber cupsole, undergirded by a traction pattern made for pivoting on the hardwood.

results.name: Nike Dunk High Syracuse (2021) (PS)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Nike Dunk High SP PS 'Syracuse’ revives one of the original colorways of the iconic ‘Be True to Your School’ series from 1985. Dressed in the signature colors of Syracuse University, the high-top carries a white leather upper with contrasting orange leather overlays at the forefoot and heel. Additional citrus accents land on the sneaker’s branding elements, including the woven tongue tag and signature Swoosh. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a pivot-point traction pattern originally designed for the hardwood.

results.name: Nike Dunk High SE All-Star (2021) (PS)
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Dunk High SE PS ‘All Star 2021’ celebrates the NBA’s midseason break with a leather upper in an eye-catching shade of green. Black patent leather overlays confer added polish to the vintage silhouette, while a circular NBA heel badge connects the shoe to its basketball roots. The high-top is mounted on a standard rubber cupsole, complete with a grippy rubber outsole originally designed for the hardwood.
